[0m[49m[39m  256, 262[0m:[39m[49m 
[0m[49m[39m  257, 263[0m:[39m[49m ## The Honest Take
[0m[49m[39m  258, 264[0m:[39m[49m 
[0m[49m[39m  259, 265[0m:[39m[49m Internal duplicate patient detection is the recipe in this category with the highest payoff-per-engineering-hour ratio. The duplicate rate in the source database is silently costing the organization money and patient safety every day, and the project to fix it pays for itself in months in most cases.
